  "description": "Product Description Finish dishwasher needs to be cleaned every month to make sure it’s running properly. This dishwasher cleaner makes cleaning your dishwasher easy. A dirty dishwasher won't give you the sparkle you're looking for. Even if you don't see it, grease and lime scale builds up on the vital parts of your dishwasher. Ingredients Contains 5-15% Non-Ionic Surfactants, Perfume Directions Preparation: How to Use Use Monthly 1 Use dishwasher cleaner when dishwasher is empty. 2 Only remove the sticker, not the cap. 3 Place bottle upside down in the bottom rack, like you would place a plate, keeping the cap closed. 4 Run the dishwasher empty, on a minimum 65°C programme. Fits all dishwashers do not add detergent Safety Warning Danger Contains Trideceth-3. Causes serious eye damage. Keep out of reach of children. Wear eye protection/face protection. If in Eyes: Rinse cautiously with water for several minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present and easy to do. Continue rinsing. Immediately call a doctor. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand. Manufacturer Contact Information Reckitt Benckiser, UK - PO Box 4044, Slough, SL1 0NS See more",
